{"tid":1769221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「(泛)民間記者會」認為要將民主陣營區選勝利延續到立法會","createTime":"2019-12-04T16:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T16:18:42.000Z","uid":202340,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a355f7980df9d9d3b9eeb8d04625c84ead43a438","tid":1769221,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"「民間記者會」認為，今屆區議會選舉中，民主陣營在議席上雖有勝利，但區議員仍需深耕細作，做好地區工作，例如要減少破壞，不再濫用區議會撥款，興建大白象工程，也要提高香港人的政治參與度。<br />\n<br />\n「民間記者會」表示，有不同抗爭方式將運動持續下去，包括將區議會選舉的勝利，延續到立法會，又認為針對制度內的不公，應繼續在街頭抗爭，亦需將力量凝聚，建立「黃色經濟圈」。<br />\n<br />\n對於美國通過《香港人權與民主法案》，「民間記者會」認為是示威者爭取回來，應繼續給予政府更多壓力，令政府不再打壓示威者。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495828-20191203.htm?fbclid=IwAR2Ozq1TCx-tu71_E5yMHP27OvobyCyfLlZCnz5IeW2_sCm8xQMU_fxzt_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495828-20191203.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2Ozq1TCx-tu71_E5yMHP27OvobyCyfLlZCnz5IeW2_sCm8xQMU_fxzt_4&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1ewoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=238ee1d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495828-20191203.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2Ozq1TCx-tu71_E5yMHP27OvobyCyfLlZCnz5IeW2_sCm8xQMU_fxzt_4&h=516e29ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495828-20191203.htm?fbclid=IwAR2Ozq1TCx-tu71_E5yMHP27OvobyCyfLlZCnz5IeW2_sCm8xQMU_fxzt_4</a>"},{"pid":"58b6f7401ee1aca03b23c4bec44e12b5b246ee23","tid":1769221,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"a4f9f531105ef21759b16931d3f7d5fd519ead98","tid":1769221,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:50:11.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下。<br />\n<br />\n[ 國際戰缐 ] 歐洲巡迴展覧團隊眾籌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b56ca8876e0a